icity as compared to filamentary memories such as\nReRAMs show the potential for a highly capable two-terminal back-end-of-line\nnon-volatile memory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Apr 2022 21:46:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-19"}
